ISLAMABAD, Mar 18 (APP):Federal ministers Wednesday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan.
Those who called on the prime minister included Minister for Economic Affairs Hamad Azhar, Minister for National Food Security Makhdoom Khusru Bakhtiar, Advisor on Finance Abdul Hafeez Sheikh, Advisor on Commerce Abdul Razak Dawood and Advisor on Institutional Reforms Dr Ishrat Hussain, PM Office media wing in a press release said.
